     <actual>
      <comment>
       <narrative xml:lang="EN">1: 25 subnational officers were trained on tracking climate finance expenditure at the sub-national level. A survey of the participants showed that 80% (20 out of 25) indicated that the knowledge from the training has improved their understanding of climate-related expenditure and will enhance how they report on such activities. In terms of gender disaggregation, 36% (9 out of 25) were females and 64% (16 out of 25) were males.

3: 13 districts participated in the first training on climate finance MRV and expenditure tracking in 2019. These comprised of 25 planning and budget officers from the 13 districts. 

4: No stakeholder engagement was held on the multi-stakeholder engagement strategy for climate finance in 2019. The target was not reached due to delays in commencing the development of the strategy.

5: No copies of the GCF Country Programme project selection criteria was published or distributed due to delays in commencing the revision of the project selection criteria.</narrative>
